nodes.name: Monyet
nodes.text: Another year, still just… a monyet.

nodes.name: Monyet
nodes.text: I've watched so many students walk these grounds... real UM students.

nodes.name: Monyet
nodes.text: To become one of them, I must face every challenge... and pass.

nodes.name: Monyet
nodes.text: Let’s do this. My journey to graduate begins—now!
